<section class="hosting">
<h1>Help improve developers in your community...</h1>

<div class="description">
  <h3>...by hosting a coderetreat in your city.</h3>
  <p>
  Hosts handle all of the logistics of organizing, finding a local sponsor,
  running a coderetreat and creating an atmosphere of fun and collaboration.
  Don't worry if you haven't hosted a coderetreat yet. We are here to support
  you and we will provide you many resources to help you organize an amazing
  event. If you are interested in hosting a coderetreat in your city for GDCR
  2014, please submit this form and we will add you to the facilitator/host
  mailing lists where you can get help from other facilitators/hosts from
  around the world.
  </p>

  <h3>...by facilitating a coderetreat in your city.</h3>
  <p>
  Facilitators guide participants through the exercises and lead the
  retrospectives. Don't worry if you haven't facilitated a coderetreat yet. We
  are here to support you! We will provide you with resources and online training
  sessions. If you are interested in facilitating/hosting a coderetreat event in
  your city for GDCR 2014, please submit this form and we will add you to the
  facilitator/host mailing lists where you can get help from other facilitators
  and hosts from around the world.
  </p>
</div>

<form action="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/formResponse?formkey=dHJCdlRUdHpXSHJBRVRSV2JUaVF4MkE6MA&amp;theme=0AX42CRMsmRFbUy03NThiZTgyMi1iNWZiLTQ1ZTUtYmJkZi00ZDMzODQ4NzA5YWI&amp;embedded=true&amp;ifq" method="POST">
  <h1>Sign Up Today!</h1>

  <div class="form-item required">
    <label for="entry_0">
      What is your name?
    </label>
    <input type="text" name="entry.0.single" value="" id="entry_0">
    <label class="help" for="entry_0"></label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item required">
    <label for="entry_1">What is your email address?</label>
    <input type="text" name="entry.1.single" value="" id="entry_1">
    <label class="help" for="entry_1">
      We&#39;ll use this email address to
      grant you access to the GDCR Google Groups and the GDCR Google Docs
      collection. We recommend you use an email address that is registered
      with google (such as a gmail address).
    </label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item required">
    <label for="entry_2">
      Where will your event be?
    </label>
    <input type="text" name="entry.2.single" value="" id="entry_2">
    <label class="help" for="entry_2">
      Either "City/Country" or "City/State" if you're in the US.
    </label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item">
    <label for="entry_6">
      What is your twitter handle?
    </label>
    <label class="help" for="entry_6"></label>
    <input type="text" name="entry.6.single" value="" id="entry_6">
  </div>
  <div class="form-item required">
    <label for="entry_12">What role are you looking for?</label>
    <div class="choices">
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="checkbox" name="entry.12.group" value="host" id="group_12_1">
        Host
      </div>
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="checkbox" name="entry.12.group" value="facilitator" id="group_12_2">
        Facilitator
      </div>
    </div>
    <label class="help" for="entry_12">
      <p>Hosts handle all of the
      logistics of organizing the event, find local sponsors, and create an
      atmosphere of fun and collaboration during the event.
      </p>
      <p>
      Facilitators guide participants through the exercises and
      lead the retrospectives.
      </p> <p>
      If you must, check both options if you plan on
      serving as both the host and the facilitator. However, we recommend that
      you take on only one role and find a friend to serve in the other
      role.
      </p>
    </label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item">
    <label for="entry_9">
      Would you like to join the GDCR discussion google group?
    </label>
    <div class="choices">
      <input type="checkbox" name="entry.9.group" checked value="Yes, please!" id="group_9_1">
      Yes, sign me up for the GDCR discussion Google Group! I want to
      collaborate with my fellow hosts and facilitators.
    </div>
    <label class="help" for="entry_9">
      Everyone who signs up as a host or facilitator
      for the Global Day of Coderetreat will be added to
      an announcements-only mailing list.
      Join the discussions Google Group if you would like to
      share ideas, ask questions, or collaborate directly
      with other GDCR hosts and facilitators.
    </label>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item">
    <label for="entry_3">
      Have you ever hosted or facilitated a coderetreat before?
    </label>

    <div class="choices">
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="checkbox" name="entry.3.group" value="Yes" id="group_3_1">
        Yes, I've hosted or facilitated before
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-item">

    <label for="entry_8">
      If so, how many coderetreats have you hosted or facilitated?
    </label>

    <input type="text" name="entry.8.single" value="" id="entry_8">
  </div>

  <div class="form-item">
    <label for="entry_4">
      Do you have a local company willing to sponsor your event?
    </label>
    <div class="choices">
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="radio" name="entry.4.group" value="Yes" id="group_4_1">
        Yes
      </div>
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="radio" name="entry.4.group" value="No" id="group_4_2">
        No
      </div>
      <div class="choice">
        <input type="radio" name="entry.4.group" value="Maybe" id="group_4_3">
        Maybe
      </div>
    </div>
    <label class="help" for="entry_4">
      Don't worry if you don't have a local sponsor yet.
      We'll gladly help you find one!
    </label>
  </div>

  <input type="hidden" name="pageNumber" value="0">
  <input type="hidden" name="backupCache" value="">

  <input class="submit button" type="submit" name="submit" value="Sign me up!">
</form>
